README file for Glade-Perl example project 

After you have installed Glade-Perl

To Build the supplied example

call (from the same directory as this README file)

    glade2perl Bus.glade
	
This should do the same as make test did 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

To run the code that you have generated, 

call (again from the same directory as this README file)

    perl -e 'use Generated::Bus; BusFrame->run'
OR  perl -e 'use Generated::SubBus; SubBusFrame->run'

Read the message on the UI for instructions.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

